body.description: 【6 Pack】3 Packs S24 Tempered Glass Screen Protectors with 3 Pack glass Camera Lens Protectors -- Only for S24 6.2Inch , Not for S24 Plus or S24 Ultra.ATTENTION: Activate the Touch Sensitivity Setting as follows,1: Open "Settings"2: Navigate to "Advanced Features"3: On the bottom, find and activate "Touch Sensitivity"and After pasting the tempered film, re-scan your fingerprint of the same finger twice at different angles to unlock more sensitively (IMPORTANTLY)*NOTE* QUICK & EASY INSTALLATION-No bubbles-Automatic Adsorption1 - Clean and dry your screen with included wet cloth and dry cloth.2 - Use "Dust absorber" to absorb any dust on screen.3 - Carefully peel off the backing of the screen protector.4 - Line up and apply the film to the screen.5 - Use your thumb to press down the edge of screen protector, make sure it adhere well.
